title: Fotodiox 8"x12" Softbox for Flash, Speedlight, Nikon SB-600, SB-700, SB-800, SB-900 SB-910, Canon Speedlite 380EX, 430EX, II, 550EX, 580EX, II, 600EX-RT, Vivita Flash, Sunpack, Nissin,Sigma, Sony, Pentax, Olympus, Panasonica Lumix Flashes
description: Fotodiox Square Flash Softbox softens the light coming from your external flash providing an even diffusion of light while staying out of the way of your lens.  Available in two sizes: 6x8” and 8x12”, the Square Softbox is helpful to on-the-go photographers.  Our Square Softbox fits dozens of flash units, including Nikon and Canon. The Softbox uses permanently attached Velcro strips to connect to the flash.  The grip surfaces keep the Square Softbox from slipping off, even during an active shoot. The Softboxes feature a premium reflective surface inside with a removable inner diffusion panel to help control how soft you want the light.
